{"title_page": "Ziaul Hoque Polash", "text_new": "{{Infobox person\n| name               = Ziaul Hoque Polash\n| image              = \n| native_name        = \u099c\u09bf\u09af\u09bc\u09be\u0989\u09b2 \u09b9\u0995 \u09aa\u09b2\u09be\u09b6\n| native_name_lang   = bn\n| birth_date         = 03 February\n| nationality        = Bangladeshi\n| occupation         = Actor , Director\n| years_active       = 2011-present\n}}\n\n'''Ziaul Hoque Polash''' is a Bangladeshi actor and director who mainly appears in Television drama and series.<ref>{{Cite news|last=|first=|url=https://www.ittefaq.com.bd/entertainment/83711/%E0%A6%A4%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%BF-%E0%A6%AF%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%96%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A8%E0%A7%87-%E0%A6%AF%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A8-%E0%A6%B8%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%96%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A8%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%87-%E0%A6%B9%E0%A6%87%E0%A6%9A%E0%A6%87|title=\u2018\u09a4\u09bf\u09a8\u09bf \u09af\u09c7\u0996\u09be\u09a8\u09c7 \u09af\u09be\u09a8 \u09b8\u09c7\u0996\u09be\u09a8\u09c7\u0987 \u09b9\u0987\u099a\u0987\u2019|date=29 August 2019|work=|access-date=|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n== Career ==\nPolash performed in [[Bachelor Point]] the most viewed tv serial drama in [[Bangladesh]] as \"Kaabila\" which was directed by Kajal Arefin Ome.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://samakal.com/entertainment/article/19082199/%E0%A6%A5%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%95%E0%A7%87-%E0%A6%95%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%B2%E0%A6%BE|title=\u09aa\u09b2\u09be\u09b6 \u09a5\u09c7\u0995\u09c7 \u0995\u09be\u09ac\u09bf\u09b2\u09be...|website=\u09b8\u09ae\u0995\u09be\u09b2|language=en|access-date=2020-04-29}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.dhakaorthoniti.com/%e0%a6%95%e0%a6%be%e0%a6%ac%e0%a6%bf%e0%a6%b2%e0%a6%be%e0%a6%b0-%e0%a6%9c%e0%a6%a8%e0%a7%8d%e0%a6%ae%e0%a6%a6%e0%a6%bf%e0%a6%a8-%e0%a6%86%e0%a6%9c/|title='\u0995\u09be\u09ac\u09bf\u09b2\u09be'\u09b0 \u099c\u09a8\u09cd\u09ae\u09a6\u09bf\u09a8 \u0986\u099c|date=2020-02-03|website=\u09a2\u09be\u0995\u09be \u0985\u09b0\u09cd\u09a5\u09a8\u09c0\u09a4\u09bf|language=en-US|access-date=20